title: Repulsion - None More Negative (Type O Negative DEMO)
description:
Cleaned up and enhanced.

This is the recording before the name change. It has 6 songs, which are in a slightly different mix than what appears on Slow, Deep and Hard, though they are vary similar.

Track list:

1. Unsuccessfully Coping with the Natural Beauty of Infidelity
2. Gravitational Constant: G = 6.67 Ã— 10âˆ’8 cmâˆ’3 gmâˆ’1 secâˆ’2
3. The Misinterpretation of Silence and its Disastrous Consequences
4. Prelude To Agony
5. Der Untermensch
6. Xero Tolerance



I could never find a good quality download anywhere, and the only source I could actually find of this actual demo was on YouTube. I downloaded it in PCM WAV, ran it through Cool Edit Pro and applied "Hard Limiter" and "Panning/Expanding" to jazz it up. I then broke it down into separate tracks and then encoded it into FLAC from the original WAV file.

I'd be more than happy to get a good first generation rip of this album, if one would be inclined. But, this sounds good on a radio, home or car. 

Please enjoy and share!
